author: Crystal Bell
title: SuperM Joins A Chaotic Group FaceTime Call For A Playful ‘Together At Home’ Performance
description: Global superstars SuperM perform their unreleased track 'With You' for Global Citizen's 'One World: Together At Home' star-studded event. The members playfully hopped on a group FaceTime call for the chaotic performance.
content: Who needs a social media AU when the members of SuperM just gave fans a glimpse into their chaotic group chat?During Global Citizen's One World: Together At Home livestream special on Saturday (April 18), social distancing wasn't keeping Baekhyun, Taemin, Kai… [+2474 chars]
